== 开发 ==

《时空幻境》发售后，乔纳森·布洛对《见证者》展开构思。2008年，布洛看到《时空幻境》大获成功，于是他结束“认真开发”的状态，开始推出新的游戏概念，每个概念都花费了数月。这些概念就是后来《见证者》的基础，布洛认为它“颇具野心并且很有挑战性”。<ref name="gamasutra interview">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/6224/catching_up_with_jonathan_blow.php|title=Catching Up With Jonathan Blow|accessdate=2010-12-06|date=2010-12-06|last=Parkin|first=Simon|publisher=UBM TechWeb|website=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101210073356/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/6224/catching_up_with_jonathan_blow.php|archivedate=2010-12-10}}</ref>因为游戏需要3D引擎，所以布洛认为这里面存在风险，他担心如果失败了，他会“跌回原点”，回到《时空幻境》成功前的生活状态<ref name="gamasutra interview" />。尽管面临着诸多挑战，布洛还是将这款游戏继续了下去，因为它是他创造过的最引人入胜的原型<ref name="gamasutra interview" />。游戏的直接开发工作于2008年底开始<ref name="gamasutra concurrent">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/39338/Indepth_Concurrent_World_Editing_On_The_Cheap.php|title=In-depth: Concurrent World Editing, On The Cheap|accessdate=2011-12-28|date=2011-12-28|last=Blow|first=Jonathan|publisher=UBM TechWeb|website=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120108064326/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/39338/Indepth_Concurrent_World_Editing_On_The_Cheap.php|archivedate=2012-01-08}}</ref>。

游戏本身依据布洛之前曾设想过但未完成的概念构建。布洛称在这个尚未完成的构想中，有一个“神奇时刻”会让游戏更令人兴奋。提炼之前概念中的“神奇时刻”并用自己的游戏和故事包装，从而形成了现在《见证者》的游戏玩法。布洛将这一时刻比作电影的[[剧透|剧透]]，拒绝披露本作的机制或其他方面的信息<ref name="gamasutra interview" /><ref name="gamasutra epiphany">{{cite web|url=http://gamasutra.com/view/news/218953/The_Witness_Modeling_epiphany.php|title=The Witness: Modeling epiphany|accessdate=2016-01-26|date=2014-06-06|last=Alexander|first=Leigh|publisher=UBM TechWeb|website=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160131120322/http://gamasutra.com/view/news/218953/The_Witness_Modeling_epiphany.php|archivedate=2016-01-31}}</ref>。迷宫面板的主意最早出自2002年，当时布洛在一个涉及法师的游戏中看到玩家会通过[[手势识别|鼠标手势]]施法，这一通过稍微变化特定手势来改变法术效果的设定在当时的电子游戏界很流行；《见证者》的故事内容就是借用于此<ref name="arstech sept2015">{{cite web|url=http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2015/09/the-man-and-the-island-wandering-through-jonathan-blows-the-witness/|title=The man and the island: Wandering through Jonathan Blow’s The Witness|accessdate=2015-09-18|date=2015-09-17|last=Machkovech|first=Sam|publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]]|website=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150918112008/http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2015/09/the-man-and-the-island-wandering-through-jonathan-blows-the-witness/|archivedate=2015-09-18}}</ref>。

《见证者》的一个目标是把电子游戏变为一种艺术形式，“探讨游戏可以实现的非语言交流的不同特色，我认为这对于了解游戏这种表现形式是很重要的”，布洛如是说<ref name="wapost review">{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/comic-riffs/wp/2016/02/02/the-witness-review-a-daunting-confounding-maddening-and-beautiful-game/|title=‘The Witness’ review: A daunting, confounding, maddening, and beautiful game|last=Byrd|first=Christopher|date=2016-02-02|newspaper=[[Washington_Post|Washington Post]]|accessdate=2016-02-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202224701/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/comic-riffs/wp/2016/02/02/the-witness-review-a-daunting-confounding-maddening-and-beautiful-game/|archivedate=2016-02-02}}</ref>。游戏的名字《见证者》取自其核心玩法，玩家在没有言语交流的情况下感知周围环境，发现谜题的含义与解决方法，1993年的游戏《[[神秘岛_(游戏)|神秘岛]]》也有类似的玩法<ref name="usatoday e3">{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/gaming/2013/06/19/the-witness-jonathan-blow-playstation-4/2435281/|title=Bearing witness to 'The Witness'|accessdate=2013-06-19|date=2013-06-19|last=Snider|first=Mike|website=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130620075158/http://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/gaming/2013/06/19/the-witness-jonathan-blow-playstation-4/2435281/|archivedate=2013-06-20}}</ref>。《神秘岛》让布洛走上了电子游戏开发的道路，而《见证者》的许多设计也在向其致敬。布洛希望解决《神秘岛》一些谜题中“像素搜索”的问题；玩家遇到虚拟机械后不明白这东西的用途，就开始狂点它的各个部分，直到后来才发现正确的方法。在《见证者》中，布洛使用迷宫面板统一了谜题的风格以避免这种混乱。所有迷宫有着共同的交互机制，游戏中的符号语言确定了规则和行为，形成了游戏谜题的核心<ref name="polygon july2015" />。岛屿被分成多个区域，以便玩家可以在一个大致位置内了解到该区域谜题风格的所有信息，这是一种“削减曾经存在于许多冒险游戏的含糊不清的东西”的手段<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2013/6/13/4427660/the-witness-preview-e3-2013|title=The Witness is an adventure-puzzle game about non-verbal communication|accessdate=2016-02-22|date=2013-06-13|last=Tach|first=Dave|publisher=Vox Media|website=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160302164150/http://www.polygon.com/2013/6/13/4427660/the-witness-preview-e3-2013|archivedate=2016-03-02}}</ref>。游戏的每一层设计都是有意义的，谜题不只是为了被解开那么简单，每一个谜题背后的点子都和其他谜题不同<ref>{{cite web | url = http://motherboard.vice.com/read/we-dont-have-the-words-to-talk-about-the-witness | title = With 100 Hours of Puzzles, 'The Witness' Is the Kind of Gamble Gaming Needs | first = Emanuel | last = Maiberg | date = 2015-10-28 | accessdate = 2015-11-02 | website = Vice | publisher = Vice Media | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151031020502/http://motherboard.vice.com/read/we-dont-have-the-words-to-talk-about-the-witness | archivedate = 2015-10-31 }}</ref><ref name="new yorker jan2016" />。

游戏的概念之一是在解谜与顿悟之间取得平衡，让玩家以一种非线性的方式自由探索《见证者》的世界。布洛意识到他需要创造一个世界来支持这些谜题，这将形成探索与解谜的对立，对他来说“有很大意义”<ref name="gamasutra bearing" />。布洛把该岛设计为[[開放世界|开放世界]]，以便玩家可以在解谜遇到困难时选择其他的谜题，避免因没能解决关键谜题而卡关。布洛说这是其他冒险游戏的一个常见问题<ref name="polygon july2015" /><ref name="gamasutra blow 2016">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/262900/Qamp_A_Jonathan_Blow_on_The_Witness_and_the_state_of_indie_games.php|title=Q&A: Jonathan Blow on The Witness and the state of indie games|accessdate=2016-01-04|date=2016-01-04|last=Pandell|first=Lexi|publisher=UBM TechWeb|website=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160106025514/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/262900/Qamp_A_Jonathan_Blow_on_The_Witness_and_the_state_of_indie_games.php|archivedate=2016-01-06}}</ref>。布洛想要清晰的展示谜题，而不再使用《时空幻境》的[[紅鯡魚|红鲱鱼]]手法<ref name="gamasutra blow 2016" />。玩家可以在无人居住的小岛上找到一些音频日志，这些音频鼓励去玩家探索；布洛尝试通过它们使玩家产生一种“在美丽地方的孤独感”。因为这些日志的找寻没有先后顺序，所以布洛希望每个玩家都可以对游戏叙事有不同的理解<ref name="gamasutra interview" />。最初，这些音频日志主要以故事为主，但布洛后来决定对信息模糊化处理，避免直接涉及游戏故事，让玩家自己思考游戏叙事的含义，这类似于《时空幻境》使用的文本元素<ref name="arstech sept2015" />。玩家解决更多的谜题后，会对游戏的故事有更具体的了解<ref name="gamasutra blow 2016" />。

由于《见证者》故事的朦胧性质，布洛避免引诱或迫使玩家通过固定动作获得成就。相反，游戏的目的是让玩家自己选择探索和了解这一世界，自己去领悟谜题<ref name="gamasutra interview" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/five-years-ago-jonathan-blow-knew-just-what-the-witnes-1755777462|title=Five Years Ago, Jonathan Blow Knew Just What The Witness Would Be|accessdate=2016-01-28|date=2016-01-28|last=Narcisse|first=Evan|publisher=Gawker Media|website=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160129011428/http://kotaku.com/five-years-ago-jonathan-blow-knew-just-what-the-witnes-1755777462|archivedate=2016-01-29}}</ref>。对于主机版，布洛也加入尽可能少的[[成就_(电子游戏)|成就]]<ref name="gamasutra interview" />。布洛还表达了对其他可能出现在主机或PC版本中的弹出式消息的担忧，他认为《见证者》是“一种微妙的游戏”，需要安静的环境音效，而这些弹出式窗口会损害这种状态<ref name="gamasutra interview" />。

布洛承认《见证者》是一款对智力水平要求比较高的游戏，而且刻意不面向广大受众开发。他认为他的做法“反任天堂”，与典型的[[任天堂|任天堂]]游戏相比，本作没有为玩家提供额外的说明<ref name="polygon july2015" />。他认为大多数游戏在开发时“把玩家当作最小公分母”，而他希望《见证者》的玩家“有好奇心并且乐于被当成聪明人”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vg247.com/2016/01/28/who-is-the-witness-for-we-asked-jonathan-blow/|title=Who is The Witness for? We asked Jonathan Blow|accessdate=2016-01-28|date=2016-01-28|last=Hillier|first=Brenna|publisher=[[Videogaming247|Videogaming247]]|website=[[VG247|VG247]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160129081116/http://www.vg247.com/2016/01/28/who-is-the-witness-for-we-asked-jonathan-blow/|archivedate=2016-01-29}}</ref>。他把对《见证者》的做法与[[托马斯·品钦|托马斯·品钦]]的《[[万有引力之虹|万有引力之虹]]》相比，因为小说“没有手-{把}-手地教你看懂每一个段落”，并且他相信他能在一款电子游戏中做到同样的效果<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/jan/27/jonathan-blow-designer-video-games-braid-the-witness|title=Jonathan Blow: 'I want to make games for people who read Gravity's Rainbow'|accessdate=2016-01-27|date=2016-01-27|last=Marsh|first=Calum|publisher=Guardian News and Media|website=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127171133/http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/jan/27/jonathan-blow-designer-video-games-braid-the-witness|archivedate=2016-01-27}}</ref>。本作的计时挑战是随机产生谜题，这些谜题被刻意设计地十分困难，意欲“测试玩家对谜题内在规则的了解有多深，以及他们对新迷宫的反应有多快”<ref name="kotaku challenge" />。

=== 资金与进度 ===
《见证者》于2009年公开。当时布洛对游戏的发行还没有明确的计划，他为游戏拨出了80万美元的预算。<ref name="new yorker jan2016" /><ref name="gamasutra bearing">{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/134819/bearing_witness.php | title = Bearing Witness | first = Christian | last = Nutt | date = 2011-08-08 | accessdate = 2016-01-25 | website = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | publisher = UBM TechWeb | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160126091305/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/134819/bearing_witness.php | archivedate = 2016-01-26 }}</ref>

布洛成立了{{Lang|en|Thekla, Inc.}}负责游戏的开发与发行<ref name="mcv witness" />。2009年12月，布洛雇佣了一名3D美术设计和一名技术程序员与他一起远程工作<ref name="gamasutra interview" />。至2015年，布洛称团队大约有8名全职成员<ref name="gamasutra concurrent" />，2011年有10到11人，最高曾达到15人<ref name="gamasutra epiphany" />。其他美术设计和程序员也为《见证者》的开发做出了些许贡献，如之前曾参与《时空幻境》美术设计工作的大卫·赫尔曼（{{Lang|en|David Hellman}}）继续进行《见证者》的概念化设计<ref name="gamasutra interview" />。其他贡献者有埃里克·厄克特（{{Lang|en|Eric Urquhart}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/braid-maker-shows-the-witness|title=Braid maker shows The Witness|accessdate=2010-03-02|date=2010-03-01|last=Purchese|first=Robert|publisher=[[AOL_Tech|AOL Tech]]|website=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100302200408/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/braid-maker-shows-the-witness|archivedate=2010-03-02}}</ref>和伊格纳西奥·卡斯塔尼奥，前者为游戏提供3D概念艺术品，而后者开发了游戏的照明和视效渲染系统<ref name="TWITNESS">{{cite web|url=http://the-witness.net/info.html|title=Graphics Tech: Precomputed Lighting|accessdate=2010-03-02|date=2010-03-01|last=Blow|first=Jonathan|publisher=Thekla, Inc.|website=The Witness|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100304231804/http://the-witness.net/info.html|archivedate=2010-03-04}}</ref>。欧索雅·斯班尤尔是一名刚毕业的图形设计师，布洛在2011年雇用了她并给予她充分的信任。她将岛上原本稀疏的图像改造成了更加生动的风景，这被纳入游戏最终成品中<ref name="polygon july2015" />。在众人的帮助下，布洛有了更多时间专注核心游戏设计，而在之前《时空幻境》的开发中，大部分工作都得由他自己做<ref name="gamasutra interview" />。

《见证者》的开发工作历史7年才得以完成<ref name="eurogamer mazes" /><ref name="GSPY">{{cite web | url = http://uk.pc.gamespy.com/pc/the-witness/1010683p1.html | title = Johnathan Blow Announces New Game | accessdate = 2010-03-02 | last = Barber | first = Tyler | date = 2009-08-04 | website = [[GameSpy|GameSpy]] | publisher = IGN Entertainment | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110204192115/http://uk.pc.gamespy.com/pc/the-witness/1010683p1.html | archivedate = 2011-02-04 }}</ref><ref name="edge blow interview">{{cite web | url = http://www.next-gen.biz/features/jonathan-blow-interview | title = Jonathan Blow interview | website = [[Edge_(magazine)|Edge]] | publisher = [[Future_Publishing|Future Publishing]] | date = 2011-09-27 | accessdate = 2011-09-28 | first = Alex | last = Wiltshire | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111103082645/http://www.next-gen.biz/features/jonathan-blow-interview | archivedate = 2011-11-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。布洛表示因为他和团队一直保持开发，游戏内容不断扩大，才导致这么长的开发时间。他本可节省时间与成本，如压缩游戏范围或使用现成的游戏引擎<ref name="polygon july2015" />，但他决定把《时空幻境》的收入（截至2014年4月共计400万美元）纳入开发成本<ref name="polygon july2015" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newyorker.com/tech/elements/the-guilt-of-the-video-game-millionaires|title=The Guilt of the Video-Game Millionaires|accessdate=2015-09-17|date=2014-04-03|last=Parkin|first=Simon|publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]]|website=[[The_New_Yorker|The New Yorker]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907111044/http://www.newyorker.com/tech/elements/the-guilt-of-the-video-game-millionaires|archivedate=2015-09-07}}</ref>。在用尽了《时空幻境》的资金后，2015年2月布洛开始寻求额外的资本，他认为无论额外开发时间的成本如何，从长远来看债务还是合理的<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2015-02-09-jon-blow-has-gone-into-debt-to-finish-the-witness|title=Jon Blow has gone into debt to finish The Witness|accessdate=2015-09-17|date=2015-02-09|last=Handrahan|first=Matthew|publisher=[[Gamer_Network|Gamer Network]]|website=GamesIndustry.biz|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150628192734/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2015-02-09-jon-blow-has-gone-into-debt-to-finish-the-witness|archivedate=2015-06-28}}</ref>。最终的开发成本估计近600万美元<ref name="wired sept2015">{{cite web | url = http://www.wired.com/2015/09/jonathan-blow-the-witness/ | title = This Sprawling Puzzle Game May Be Your Next Obsession | first = Bo | last = Moore | date = 2015-09-17 | accessdate = 2015-09-17 | website = [[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]] | publisher = [[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150918224617/http://www.wired.com/2015/09/jonathan-blow-the-witness/ | archivedate = 2015-09-18 }}</ref><ref name="new yorker jan2016">{{cite web | url = http://www.newyorker.com/tech/elements/the-prickly-genius-of-jonathan-blow | title = The Prickly Genius of Jonathan Blow | first = Simon | last = Parkin | date = 2016-01-29 | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | website = [[The_New_Yorker|The New Yorker]] | publisher = [[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160130095216/http://www.newyorker.com/tech/elements/the-prickly-genius-of-jonathan-blow | archivedate = 2016-01-30 }}</ref><ref name="verge jan2016">{{cite web | url = http://www.theverge.com/2016/1/26/10828070/the-witness-jonathan-blow-thekla-interview-ps4-pc | title = The creators of The Witness on how they made a 100-hour puzzle game | first = Andrew | last = Webster | date = 2016-01-26 | accessdate = 2016-01-26 | website = [[The_Verge|The Verge]] | publisher = Vox Media | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160126150959/http://www.theverge.com/2016/1/26/10828070/the-witness-jonathan-blow-thekla-interview-ps4-pc | archivedate = 2016-01-26 }}</ref>。虽然布洛认为由于缺乏资金或主要发行商的支持，《见证者》是一款独立游戏，但他也觉得从该项目所花的时间和成本来看，游戏已接近[[AAA_(电子游戏产业)|3A]]大作的水准，这代表了行业一种新型游戏开发方式<ref name="mcv witness" /><ref name="engadget jan16">{{cite web|url=http://www.engadget.com/2016/01/21/traveling-through-time-with-braid-creator-jonathan-blow/|title=Traveling through time with 'Braid' creator Jonathan Blow|accessdate=2016-01-21|date=2016-01-21|last=Conditt|first=Jessica|publisher=[[AOL_Tech|AOL Tech]]|website=[[Engadget|Engadget]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160121193259/http://www.engadget.com/2016/01/21/traveling-through-time-with-braid-creator-jonathan-blow/|archivedate=2016-01-21}}</ref>。

《见证者》使用布洛和团队自行研发的引擎，这占用了相当多的开发时间<ref name="polygon july2015" /><ref name="wired sept2015" />。布洛不使用其他现有的如[[Unity_(游戏引擎)|Unity]]等引擎是因为自家引擎可以受到完全控制<ref name="wired sept2015" />。作为一个紧凑的游戏世界，游戏中的岛屿被视为一个区域，这简化了游戏性和引擎开发<ref name="gamasutra concurrent" />。

2013年11月，布洛与两名[[威尔乌|Valve公司]]开发者会面，后者展示了他们即将推出的{{Le|SteamVR|SteamVR}}技术。布洛发现这有利于提升玩家探索岛屿的能力，所以在《见证者》中，开发团队为即将到来的[[虚拟现实|虚拟现实]]（VR）硬件提供了支持<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/1/24/5342562/valve-vr-jonathan-blow-the-witness|title=How Valve tech convinced Jonathan Blow to add VR to The Witness|accessdate=2016-02-16|date=2014-01-24|last=Tach|first=Dave|publisher=Vox Media|website=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160301052621/http://www.polygon.com/2014/1/24/5342562/valve-vr-jonathan-blow-the-witness|archivedate=2016-03-01}}</ref>。尽管游戏发行时为VR提供了技术支持，但《见证者》并没有采用虚拟现实方式设计，程序员安德鲁·史密斯表示如果头部运动可以与身体运动分离的话，许多谜题都可以“瞒天过海”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vg247.com/2016/02/15/playing-the-witness-in-vr-is-far-from-optimal-vr-version-problematic/|title=Playing The Witness in VR “is far from optimal”, VR version “problematic”|accessdate=2016-02-15|date=2016-02-15|last=Saed|first=Sharid|publisher=[[Videogaming247|Videogaming247]]|website=[[VG247|VG247]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216092530/http://www.vg247.com/2016/02/15/playing-the-witness-in-vr-is-far-from-optimal-vr-version-problematic/|archivedate=2016-02-16}}</ref>。

=== 设计、艺术及音效 ===
《见证者》岛屿的设计与布局自游戏开发初始就已基本定型，团队的主要工作是将具体的谜题加入世界，并细化景观和其他美术设计。[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]网站的编辑山姆·马克科维奇（{{Lang|en|Sam Machkovech}}）于2012年和2015年两度试玩此游戏，指出海岛一直保持了那个样子<ref name="arstech sept2015" />。游戏世界设计的一个方面是使用电线连通全岛，把面板谜题连接到控制机制上。布洛发现这些在游戏最开始为玩家提供了帮助，“非常清晰”地为他们指明了下一步的行动方向，但他也发现这样也使游戏模式过于重复<ref name="gamasutra bearing" />。在开发过程中，电线的设计仍然被保留下来，但设计师加强了隐蔽性，以引导玩家发现潜在的目标<ref name="gamasutra bearing" />。

[[File:The_witness_gameplay_screenshot.png|thumb]]
团队对岛上的解谜、探索和叙事元素进行了合理搭配，同时避免因给予玩家过多自由而让他们“无从选择”，不知道下一步要去哪<ref name="gamasutra bearing" />。据美术设计路易斯·安东尼奥的说法，布洛想让玩家第一眼就能看到山，让玩家知道这是他们的终极目标。游戏最初把玩家放置在一个废弃的地堡内，但玩家在离开地堡时并未面对着山。虽然团队试图移动并旋转地堡空间，但为配合游戏的其它部分，这一设计最终被废弃，取而代之的是一个简洁的带有少量内饰元素的空间，玩家来到外部环境时高山也会一览无遗。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/265933/Find_out_how_the_world_of_The_Witness_was_brought_to_life.php|title=Find out how the world of The Witness was brought to life|accessdate=2016-02-16|date=2016-02-16|last=Kerr|first=Chris|publisher=UBM TechWeb|website=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216132543/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/265933/Find_out_how_the_world_of_The_Witness_was_brought_to_life.php|archivedate=2016-02-16}}</ref>这一开篇区域也算是游戏的教程，帮助玩家了解游戏的基本机制，那就是他们必须在解谜和探索之间切换。Thekla花费大量时间完善细节，在没有语言说明的情况下让玩家明白游戏原理<ref name="destructoid tutorial">{{cite web|url=https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2016/02/19/the-witness-tutorial/|title=How does The Witness teach without words?|accessdate=2016-02-19|date=2016-02-19|last=Smith|first=Adam|publisher=Positive Internet|website=[[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160220093637/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2016/02/19/the-witness-tutorial/|archivedate=2016-02-20}}</ref>。团队利用彩色对比和天然及人造结构突出显示那些玩家将要前往的区域<ref name="art entrypath" />。布洛想要游戏艺术以鲜艳的色彩和高饱和度为特色，为玩家呈现一种乐观的色调，不过游戏后期的设定就没有那么明亮了。他还希望确保游戏世界中的所有元素足够显眼，避免游戏中的视觉噪声干扰解谜<ref name="gamasutra blow 2016" />。为了实现这一点，他和团队经常要复查游戏，找出那些需要加强视觉吸引的元素；在这一过程中，一些早期加入的元素在最终成品游戏中因不合适而被去除<ref name="gamasutra epiphany" />。

游戏艺术风格较为简洁，物体被省去了细节但保持了整体形状，使其清晰可辨。安东尼奥称这一灵感来源于现实世界的摄影和艺术品以及《风之旅人》、《[[軍團要塞2|军团要塞2]]》和《[[镜之边缘|镜之边缘]]》的游戏环境<ref name="gdc art">{{cite web|url=http://gdcvault.com/play/1020552/The-Art-of-The|title=The Art of the Witness|accessdate=2016-01-26|date=2014-03-20|last=Antonio|first=Luis|publisher=UBM TechWeb|website=GDC Vault|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160201062432/http://gdcvault.com/play/1020552/The-Art-of-The|archivedate=2016-02-01}}</ref>。他们还希望确保玩家可以根据周围的树木种类等可视外观认清岛屿的面积，并保证在简化事物的同时使它们有明显的区别<ref name="gamasutra artsimple">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/228977/The_Witness_artist_reminds_us_to_keep_it_simple_stupid.php|title=The Witness artist reminds us to keep it simple, stupid|accessdate=2016-01-27|date=2014-10-31|last=Wawro|first=Alex|publisher=UBM TechWeb|website=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160128101554/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/228977/The_Witness_artist_reminds_us_to_keep_it_simple_stupid.php|archivedate=2016-01-28}}</ref>。布洛的团队还聘用了一个现实世界的建筑设计公司Fourm设计工作室（{{Lang|en|Fourm Design Studio}}）和一个景观设计团队弗莱彻工作室（{{Lang|en|Fletcher Studio}}）协助《见证者》的环境开发<ref name="gdc art" />。据Fourm创始人迪安娜·范·布伦（{{Lang|en|Deanna Van Buren}}）所述，他们基于三个不同文明时期的特点开发了各种人工和耕地区域，后期的文明建立在较早文明结构之上，并根据需要使用这些结构<ref name="gamasutra architecture">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/blogs/DeannaVanBuren/20151012/254238/Architecture_in_Video_Games_Designing_for_Impact.php|title=Architecture in Video Games: Designing for Impact|accessdate=2016-01-25|date=2015-10-12|last=Van Buren|first=Deanna|publisher=UBM TechWeb|website=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160128075538/http://www.gamasutra.com/blogs/DeannaVanBuren/20151012/254238/Architecture_in_Video_Games_Designing_for_Impact.php|archivedate=2016-01-28}}</ref>。他们工作室为主要开发团队设计原则，让团队得出自己的想法<ref name="gamasutra architecture" />。布洛说建筑师的指导和建议对岛的构建有所帮助，“让人感觉岛屿更逼真，因为细节非常到位，你无需思考就可立即使用。”<ref name="verge jan2016" />布洛给出岛上处于老化的不同状态的建筑的示例，但都把它设计成详细完整的结构，并故意做成被损毁的样子；最后的结构保留了逻辑上一致的细节，如木头的残骸支撑着腐朽的楼梯<ref name="destructoid tutorial" />。

[[File:Marin-County-and-Angel-Island.jpg|thumb]]（前景）采集。]]
最终的成品游戏附带的音乐很少，而是依赖由侘寂声音（{{Lang|en|Wabi Sabi Sound}}）打造的环境音效。布洛觉得加入音乐只会适得其反<ref name="vg247 nomusic">{{cite web|url=http://www.vg247.com/2015/11/20/the-witness-long-screenshot-trailer-emphasises-music-free-sound-design/|title=The Witness “Long Screenshot” trailer emphasises music-free sound design|accessdate=2015-11-22|date=2015-11-20|last=Hillier|first=Brenna|publisher=[[Videogaming247|Videogaming247]]|website=[[VG247|VG247]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121164732/http://www.vg247.com/2015/11/20/the-witness-long-screenshot-trailer-emphasises-music-free-sound-design/|archivedate=2015-11-21}}</ref>。因为岛上缺乏其他动物类生命，所以环境音效也变得难以加入，这也让玩家知道他们在岛上是多么地孤单<ref name="vg247 nomusic" />。大部分环境音效由侘寂声音的安德鲁·拉基（{{Lang|en|Andrew Lackey}}）记录，他在旧金山湾[[天使島|天使岛]]周围捕捉到了这些声音<ref name="gamasutra sound">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/264301/Why_all_the_audio_for_The_Witness_was_recorded_on_location.php|title=Why all the audio for The Witness was recorded on location|accessdate=2016-01-26|date=2016-01-26|last=Gardiner|first=Bryan|publisher=UBM TechWeb|website=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127100525/http://gamasutra.com/view/news/264301/Why_all_the_audio_for_The_Witness_was_recorded_on_location.php|archivedate=2016-01-27}}</ref>。拉基把各种音效分层，可随玩家在岛上位置的改变而变化，同时还支持从一个环境到下一个环境的无缝过渡<ref name="gamasutra sound" />。

== 营销与发行 ==
布洛在2010年的西雅图游戏展（{{Lang|en|Penny Arcade Expo}}）上悄悄向公众展出了这款游戏，他与展台保持着距离，看着前来试玩的人的反应<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/news/witness-quietly-debuted-pax|title=The Witness Quietly Debuted at PAX|accessdate=2010-09-07|date=2010-09-07|last=Watts|first=Steve|publisher=IGN Entertainment|website=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111027185723/http://www.1up.com/news/witness-quietly-debuted-pax|archivedate=2011-10-27}}</ref>。展会后，布洛和[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]的史蒂芬·托蒂洛（{{Lang|en|Stephen Totilo}}）透露了《见证者》，托蒂洛看到并试玩了此游戏， 但当时并未提及<ref name="kotaku pax" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://the-witness.net/news/?p=471|title=We showed The Witness secretly at PAX… in plain sight.|accessdate=2010-09-06|date=2010-09-06|last=Blow|first=Jonathan|publisher=Thekla, Inc.|website=The Witness|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100908212930/http://the-witness.net/news/?p=471|archivedate=2010-09-08}}</ref>。在展会试玩游戏或看到Kotaku文章中的游戏画面的玩家后来担心《见证者》仅仅是一款解决一系列迷宫的游戏。布洛重申游戏中不仅只有迷宫，游戏的部分视频不能够说明“在解谜过程中玩家是怎么想的”。<ref name="eurogamer mazes" />

在2010年游戏展出时，布洛预计它将于Microsoft Windows和iOS设备发行，游戏机平台尚未确定，可能包括[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]和[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]<ref name="GSPY" />。当年末，布洛重申了他的立场，称考虑到额外的编程时间量和主机平台的限制，最初发行时将不会有主机版本<ref name="eurogamer mazes" /><ref name="edge blow interview" />。2011年11月，布洛雇用了两名程序员，并重新考虑了主机版本的发行；虽然他无法承诺在最初发行主机版，但因为有新的人手加入，游戏推出时将可能会有主机版，而且也会在晚些时候登陆其他主机平台<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2011/12/02/is-the-witness-coming-to-consoles.aspx|title=Is The Witness Coming To Consoles?|accessdate=2011-12-05|date=2011-12-02|last=Miller|first=Matt|publisher=[[GameStop|GameStop]]|website=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111205024156/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2011/12/02/is-the-witness-coming-to-consoles.aspx|archivedate=2011-12-05}}</ref>。随着游戏开发的逐渐深入，游戏引擎也变得更加复杂，布洛决定放弃[[遊戲機歷史_(第七世代)|第七代主机版]]的开发，理由是它们的“系统规格相对较低”<ref name="kotaku ps4 limited" />。

2012年左右，[[遊戲機歷史_(第八世代)|下一代主机]]问世，布洛和团队开始寻找机会<ref name="kotaku ps4 limited" />。因为相同的原因他们砍掉了[[Wii_U|Wii U]]，并决定在PlayStation 4和Xbox One平台之间做出选择。与微软相比，此时索尼已能提供硬件信息与开发套件，公司还找了布洛等独立开发者了解即将推出的PlayStation 4。权衡之下，布洛最终选择了PlayStation平台。<ref name="polygon july2015" /><ref name="kotaku ps4 limited">{{cite web | url = http://kotaku.com/5986093/how-the-witness-became-a-ps4-game-and-why-pcios-owners-can-remain-happy | title = How The Witness Became a PS4 Game (And Why PC/iOS Owners Can Remain Happy) | first = Stephan | last = Tolito | date = 2013-02-21 | accessdate = 2013-02-21 | website = [[Kotaku|Kotaku]] | publisher = Gawker Media | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130225070117/http://kotaku.com/5986093/how-the-witness-became-a-ps4-game-and-why-pcios-owners-can-remain-happy | archivedate = 2013-02-25 }}</ref><ref name="PLYGN">{{cite web | url = http://www.polygon.com/2013/2/20/4010968/the-witness-playstation-4-jon-blow | title = The Witness from Jonathan Blow to debut on PS4 as timed console exclusive | accessdate = 2013-02-20 | last = McWhertor | first = Michael | date = 2013-02-20 | website = [[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]] | publisher = Vox Media | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130224001442/http://www.polygon.com/2013/2/20/4010968/the-witness-playstation-4-jon-blow | archivedate = 2013-02-24 }}</ref><ref name="ps4 exclusivity">{{cite web | url = http://kotaku.com/5986093/how-the-witness-became-a-ps4-game-and-why-pcios-owners-can-remain-happy | title = How The Witness Became a PS4 Game | website = [[Kotaku|Kotaku]] | publisher = Gawker Media | date = 2013-02-21 | accessdate = 2015-04-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141224063948/http://kotaku.com/5986093/how-the-witness-became-a-ps4-game-and-why-pcios-owners-can-remain-happy | archivedate = 2014-12-24 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2015/09/how-sony-snagged-jonathan-blows-the-witness-away-from-the-xbox-one/ | title = How Sony snagged Jonathan Blow’s The Witness away from the Xbox One | date = 2015-09-17 | accessdate = 2015-09-18 | first = Sam | last = Machkovech | website = [[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]] | publisher = [[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150920014951/http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2015/09/how-sony-snagged-jonathan-blows-the-witness-away-from-the-xbox-one/ | archivedate = 2015-09-20 }}</ref>布洛也申明这一决定没有任何金钱交易<ref name="kotaku ps4 limited" />。《见证者》计划于2013年随PlayStation 4首发上市，且PS4为限时独占平台。Windows和iOS版本计划于PlayStation4版同期发行，不能再有开发延期的事情发生。如果团队决定开发的话，其他主机版将会于晚些时候发行<ref name="kotaku ps4 limited" />。

2013年，《见证者》仍在开发中，布洛和团队还在不断改进和调整游戏，2013年的发布计划落空<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/08/20/jonathan-blows-the-witness-is-nearing-completion|title=Jonathan Blow's The Witness is Nearly Completion|accessdate=2016-01-26|date=2014-08-20|last=Macy|first=Seth G.|website=[[IGN|IGN]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202233955/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/08/20/jonathan-blows-the-witness-is-nearing-completion|archivedate=2016-02-02}}</ref>。2015年9月，布洛宣布游戏发售日定于2016年1月26日，登陆PlayStation 4和Microsoft Windows，iOS版本则于短期内跟进发行<ref name="polygon july2015" />。发行前，[[ESRB|ESRB]]把游戏标上了Xbox One字样，但布洛澄清道目前他们在该平台没有发售计划<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2016/1/18/10786184/the-witness-xbox-one-esrb-rating|title=The Witness rated for Xbox One, but developer currently has 'no plans' for it|accessdate=2016-01-18|date=2016-01-18|last=Sarkar|first=Samit|website=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160118202051/http://www.polygon.com/2016/1/18/10786184/the-witness-xbox-one-esrb-rating|archivedate=2016-01-18}}</ref>。游戏发行前一星期，布洛宣布游戏将定价40美元，称这“公正地反映出了游戏的本质”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/feb/07/is-price-of-game-ever-really-right-the-witness|title=Is the price of a video game ever really right?|accessdate=2016-02-07|date=2016-02-07|last=Parkin|first=Simon|publisher=Guardian News and Media|website=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160207093231/http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/feb/07/is-price-of-game-ever-really-right-the-witness|archivedate=2016-02-07}}</ref>。有批评认为这一价格对于独立游戏来说过高。一些游戏网站编者认为以布洛曾公布的百小时的游玩时间来说，这一价格是合理的。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.pcgamer.com/the-witness-preorders-go-live-with-a-40-price-tag/ | title = The Witness preorders go live with a $40 price tag | first = Andy | last = Chalk | date = 2016-01-19 | accessdate = 2016-01-19 | website = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] | publisher = [[Future_US|Future US]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160121221217/http://www.pcgamer.com/the-witness-preorders-go-live-with-a-40-price-tag/ | archivedate = 2016-01-21 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://kotaku.com/jonathan-blow-s-next-puzzle-game-the-witness-arrives-1753835123 | title = Jonathan Blow’s next puzzle game, The Witness, arrives January 26 | website = [[Kotaku|Kotaku]] | publisher = Gawker Media | first = Patrick | last = Klepek | date = 2016-01-19 | accessdate = 2016-01-19 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160119234304/http://kotaku.com/jonathan-blow-s-next-puzzle-game-the-witness-arrives-1753835123 | archivedate = 2016-01-19 }}</ref>开发团队制作了三个“长截图”视频来推广游戏，短片受到实验电影《[[失衡生活|失衡生活]]》的启发，缓慢展现了全岛风貌，没有任何描述<ref name="artblog promo">{{cite web | url = http://www.artofluis.com/3d-work/the-art-of-the-witness/release-trailer-and-long-screenshots/ | title = The Art of 'The Witness' | first = Luis | last = Antonio | date = 2016 | website = Art of Luis | accessdate = 2016-02-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160213041321/http://www.artofluis.com/3d-work/the-art-of-the-witness/release-trailer-and-long-screenshots/ | archivedate = 2016-02-13 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.vg247.com/2016/01/04/the-witness-gets-another-beautifully-quiet-long-screenshot-trailer/ | title = The Witness gets another beautifully quiet “Long Screenshot” trailer | first = Brenna | last = Hillier | website = [[VG247|VG247]] | publisher = [[Videogaming247|Videogaming247]] | date = 2016-01-04 | accessdate = 2016-02-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160222004734/http://www.vg247.com/2016/01/04/the-witness-gets-another-beautifully-quiet-long-screenshot-trailer/ | archivedate = 2016-02-22 }}</ref>。

布洛表示他们一直在与出版商讨论游戏的实体发行，但因生产和销售需要大量时间，他们决定一开始先不这么做。随着游戏完成并以数字版发行，他们正致力于可能的零售版本。<ref name="mcv witness">{{cite web | url = http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/the-witness-isn-t-an-indie-game/0162736 | title = "The Witness isn't an indie game" | first = Alex | last = Calvin | date = 2016-02-18 | accessdate = 2016-02-18 | website = Market for Home Computing and Video Games | publisher = New Bay Media | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160219113802/http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/the-witness-isn-t-an-indie-game/0162736 | archivedate = 2016-02-19 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.pcgamer.com/a-boxed-edition-of-the-witness-is-seeming-likely/ | title = A boxed edition of The Witness is "seeming likely" | first = Andy | last = Chalk | date = 2015-12-23 | accessdate = 2016-01-03 | website = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] | publisher = [[Future_US|Future US]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151227000227/http://www.pcgamer.com/a-boxed-edition-of-the-witness-is-seeming-likely/ | archivedate = 2015-12-27 }}</ref>游戏发行后，一些玩家表示他们得了[[晕动病|晕动病]]，因为游戏运用了窄视场，玩家在走路时的视点也会晃动。布洛称他们正在做一个补丁，以便让玩家调整视场，禁用头部晃动，选择更快速的移动。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-02-01-does-the-witness-make-you-feel-sick | title = Does The Witness make you feel sick? | last = Yin-Poole | first = Wesley | date = 2016-02-01 | website = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | publisher = [[Gamer_Network|Gamer Network]] | accessdate = 2016-02-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160201233205/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-02-01-does-the-witness-make-you-feel-sick | archivedate = 2016-02-01 }}</ref>

2016年8月，布洛证实游戏的Xbox One版本计划于2016年9月13日发行，iOS版本仍在计划中，他们在开发中需要降低画面质量以及探讨另一种控制方案<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/08/23/the-witness-for-xbox-one-announced | title = The Witness for Xbox One Announced | first = Chloi | last = Rad | date = 2016-08-23 | accessdate = 2016-08-23 | website = IGN | publisher = IGN | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160823171246/http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/08/23/the-witness-for-xbox-one-announced | archivedate = 2016-08-23 }}</ref>。2017年1月16日，适用于[[SHIELD_Android_TV|SHIELD Android TV]]的[[Android|Android]]版本于2017年1月16日开启数字下载<ref>{{cite web|title=Play the Award-Winning Puzzle Adventure, The Witness, Now Available on NVIDIA SHIELD TV|url=https://shield.nvidia.com/blog/the-witness-now-available|website=SHIELD Blog|accessdate=2017-02-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216125626/https://shield.nvidia.com/blog/the-witness-now-available|archivedate=2017-02-16}}</ref>。iOS版于2017年9月20日发行<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.destructoid.com/the-witness-is-out-for-ios-and-it-s-ten-bucks-462370.phtml | title = The Witness is out for iOS and it's ten bucks | first = Jordan | last = Devore | date = 2017-09-21 | accessdate = 2017-09-21 | work = [[Destructoid|Destructoid]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170924073727/https://www.destructoid.com/the-witness-is-out-for-ios-and-it-s-ten-bucks-462370.phtml | archivedate = 2017-09-24 }}</ref>。

