《见证者》发行后受到了游戏界的一致好评。根据评分汇总网站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]的统计，[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]和[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]版得分均为87/100<ref name="MC-PC" /><ref name="MC-PS4" />。

[[IGN|IGN]]的克洛伊·拉德（{{Lang|en|Chloi Rad}}）给予游戏满分10分的好评，称这是“一款外表魅力，内在充满力量，有着机智解密设计的探索游戏，里面包含了许多秘密等你去挖掘。”<ref name="IGN" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamersky.com/news/201601/709706.shtml|title=《见证者》IGN 10分！开年必玩的清新解谜佳作|accessdate=2016-05-23|author=|date=2016-01-26|publisher=[[游民星空|游民星空]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160419000359/http://www.gamersky.com/news/201601/709706.shtml|archivedate=2016-04-19}}</ref>[[VG247|VG247]]的布伦纳·希利尔（{{Lang|en|Brenna Hillier}}）称赞游戏使用第一人称视角去呈现本来可能只是一系列简单谜题的游戏，他还对谜题陡峭的[[學習曲線|学习曲线]]留下了深刻印象，“在你探索了附近的位置后，你会发现那些令人费解、难以应对的谜题融入到了一些简单的练习中。”<ref name="vg247 review">{{cite web|url=https://www.vg247.com/2016/01/25/the-witness-review/|title=The Witness Review – Do yourself a favour: don’t use a guide|accessdate=2016-01-25|date=2016-01-25|last=Hiller|first=Brenna|publisher=[[Videogaming247|Videogaming247]]|website=[[VG247|VG247]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127023724/http://www.vg247.com/2016/01/25/the-witness-review/|archivedate=2016-01-27}}</ref>《[[偏锋杂志|偏锋杂志]]》的亚伦·里奇奥（{{Lang|en|Aaron Riccio}}）认为玩家来到山里后，情况会发生“尖锐的转变”，那里的谜题所在的环境更简陋，迷惑性更高<ref name="slant review" />。

《连线》的杰克·曼西（{{Lang|en|Jake Muncy}}）指出缺乏任何叙事或游戏指导可能会引起玩家的反弹<ref name="wired review">{{cite web|url=http://www.wired.com/2016/01/the-witness-review/|title=The Witness is Driving Me Insane|accessdate=2016-01-25|date=2016-01-25|last=Muncy|first=Jack|publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]]|website=[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160125172033/http://www.wired.com/2016/01/the-witness-review/|archivedate=2016-01-25}}</ref>。此外，曼西认为虽然布洛把游戏与《[[万有引力之虹|万有引力之虹]]》相提并论，但与小说引人入胜的情节相比，它未能为岛屿创造栩栩如生的环境<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wired.com/2016/02/the-witness/|title=Now That I Beat the Witness, I See What's Wrong With It|accessdate=2016-02-11|date=2016-02-11|last=Muncy|first=Jake|publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]]|website=[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160211192749/http://www.wired.com/2016/02/the-witness|archivedate=2016-02-11}}</ref>。[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]的奥里·威尔士（{{Lang|en|Oli Welsh}}）称赞游戏的谜题为玩家提供了无数的“[[尤里卡_(词语)|尤里卡]]”时刻，觉得本作是《[[哥德堡变奏曲|哥德堡变奏曲]]》的电子游戏版，但觉得谜题有些故意使其费解的意味，而且缺乏社区讨论<ref name="eurogamer review">{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-01-25-the-witness-review|title=The Witness review|accessdate=2016-01-26|date=2016-01-25|last=Welsh|first=Oli|website=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160126003337/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-01-25-the-witness-review|archivedate=2016-01-26}}</ref>。[[Polygon|Polygon]]的贾斯汀·麦克尔罗伊（{{Lang|en|Justin McElroy}}）称游戏“令人振奋也让人懊恼”，他批评有些谜题的解决时间过长，表示这会让一些缺乏耐心的玩家走捷径作弊<ref name="Polygon review" />。[[US_Gamer|US Gamer]]的鲍勃·麦基（{{Lang|en|Bob Mackey}}）对游戏的批评最多，尽管最初他称赞了游戏的视觉效果和设定，但麦基觉得谜题非常困难，“有太多的东西会给我错误的反馈”，并表示“布洛也许对他的工作有点过于着迷”<ref name="us gamer review">{{cite web|url=http://www.usgamer.net/articles/the-witness-playstation-4-review-in-progress-cast-away|title=The Witness PlayStation 4 Review: Cast Away|accessdate=2016-02-19|date=2016-01-28|last=Mackey|first=Bob|publisher=[[Gamer_Network|Gamer Network]]|website=[[US_Gamer|US Gamer]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160217132412/http://www.usgamer.net/articles/the-witness-playstation-4-review-in-progress-cast-away|archivedate=2016-02-17}}</ref>。

评论者为《见证者》的故事含义提出了多种理论<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-02-13-nobody-is-sure-what-the-witness-is-about|title=Nobody is sure what The Witness is about|accessdate=2016-02-19|date=2016-02-19|last=Matulef|first=Jeffrey|publisher=[[Gamer_Network|Gamer Network]]|website=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160220095420/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-02-13-nobody-is-sure-what-the-witness-is-about|archivedate=2016-02-20}}</ref>。[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]的大卫·罗伯特（David Robert）认为游戏的本质是顿悟，属[[知识论|知识论]]的范畴。“你旅程的终点变为开端，开端又导向终点——这是顿悟特有的循环”。<ref name="gamesradar meaning" />

游戏发行一周后，布洛称《见证者》的销量已经接近《时空幻境》发行一年的销量<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.destructoid.com/the-witness-is-already-almost-outselling-braid-s-entire-first-year-337944.phtml|title=The Witness is already almost outselling Braid's entire first year|accessdate=2016-01-31|date=2016-01-31|last=Parlock|first=Joe|publisher=ModernMethod|website=[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160131170927/http://www.destructoid.com/the-witness-is-already-almost-outselling-braid-s-entire-first-year-337944.phtml|archivedate=2016-01-31}}</ref>。后来他明确指出首周销量超过10万，销售总额超过500万美元，有望收支相抵。Thekla将考虑把游戏移植到其他平台，可能有[[iOS|iOS]]、[[Android|Android]]、[[OS_X|OS X]]和Xbox One<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/265008/The_Witness_has_grossed_over_5_million_selling_100k_in_a_week.php | title = The Witness has grossed over $5 million, selling 100k+ in a week | last = Nutt | first = Christian | date = 2016-02-02 | website = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | publisher = UBM TechWeb | accessdate = 2016-02-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160204093401/http://gamasutra.com/view/news/265008/The_Witness_has_grossed_over_5_million_selling_100k_in_a_week.php | archivedate = 2016-02-04 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-witness-sells-100000-copies-xbox-one-version-b/1100-6434441/ | title = The Witness Sells 100,000 Copies, Xbox One Version Being Considered | first = Eddie | last = Makuch | date = 2016-02-02 | website = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | publisher = [[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] | accessdate = 2016-02-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160204215710/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-witness-sells-100000-copies-xbox-one-version-b/1100-6434441/ | archivedate = 2016-02-04 }}</ref>。在发行期间，布洛称《见证者》的Windows版本成为一些非法[[BitTorrent_(协议)|BitTorrent]]网站的热门，下载量可与《时空幻境》相媲美。他决定放弃为本作使用强大的[[数字版权管理|数字版权管理]]，因为他相信“人们应该自由地支配一些东西”，但他也说可能会改变主意，对“可能发生于下一部作品的”软件[[盗版|盗版]]进行限制<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-witness-is-being-pirated-a-lot-dev-says/1100-6434309/|title=The Witness Is Being Pirated a Lot, Dev Says|accessdate=2016-01-29|date=2016-01-29|last=Makuch|first=Eddie|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130145210/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-witness-is-being-pirated-a-lot-dev-says/1100-6434309/|archivedate=2016-01-30}}</ref>。

